room_title: Escape room "The Circus" by D.O.A. Room Escape in Wisconsin Dells
room_address: 350 E Hiawatha Dr Wisconsin Dells, WI 53965
room_description:
Step right up! Step right up! Boys and girls and children of all ages, welcome to "The Greatest Show on Earth". 

Did you know that back in 1884,  Baraboo, Wisconsin was the founding place of what became the legendary Ringling Bros. and Barnum & Bailey Circus? (That's not too far from here!)

Inside our bright and colorful Circus Room, the Big Top Performance is about to begin but all of the circus acts are lost! Players must find them in time for the show to begin.
